Privacy Policy for Skyepie
Last updated: [19/09/2025]

Skyepie is a simple weather app that displays forecast data, rain and cloud maps, and allows users to adjust appearance settings.

Data collection
Skyepie does not collect, store, or share any personal information. No accounts are required.

Data use
Weather data comes from third-party weather APIs. Requests are made directly from the app to the weather service. No identifying information is sent.
Data is provided by OpenWeather

Ads
Skyepie does not display ads.

Children
This app is suitable for general audiences. It is not specifically directed at children under 13.

Contact
For questions, contact: [antpez@outlook.com]